Description:
    Generate a YAML file for store configuration data.
    After set data get the value with:

    AppConfig.name    
    

Example:
    rails g easyup:config

    This will create:
        config/initializer/config.rb
        config/app_config.yml

    rails g easyup:config contact

    This will create:
        config/initializer/config.rb
        config/contact_config.yml

    If the generator was alredy used, config/initializer/config.rb will not create
    but the necessary content for load configuration file will append to it.

